## AUDIT TRAIL

When review IS independent, generate a JSON audit record mapping to:
- NIST SP 800-53 AC-5
- ISO 27001 A.6.1.2
- SOX Section 404
- PCI-DSS 6.3
- NIST SSDF PW.7
- OWASP LLM Top 10 (LLM08)
- SOC 2 CC6.1
